==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Half-blooded
<hw>Half"-blood`ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Proceeding from
a male and female of different breeds or races; having only one parent
of good stock; <as>as, a <ex>half-blooded</ex> sheep</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Degenerate; mean.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Half-boot</ent>⟦br⟧
